# ==========================================
# Code Composer Studio (CCS) Build Outputs
# ==========================================
# Ignore the entire build output directories 
**/Debug/
**/Release/
**/configPkg/

# Ignore specific compiler/linker generated binary and map files
*.obj
*.out
*.map
*.txt
*.hex
*.bin

# ==========================================
# Eclipse / CCS Local User Configurations
# ==========================================
# Ignore local launch configurations and target execution histories
**/.launches/
**/.local/
**/.xdchelp
**/*.bak
**/.tmp

# Ignore local developer-specific layout settings 
.metadata/
RemoteSystemsTempFiles/
.crf

# ==========================================
#  KEEP Crucial Project Metadata
# ==========================================
# CCS needs these files to recognize folders as valid projects.
!**/.project
!**/.cproject
!**/.settings/